CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 2, 1945, pg. 25, reads: "Presidents Day - Mrs. Evelyn Burks, president of the FDE Steel Workers Club, was honored with a birthday party recently by the members of the club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman holding twenty-five dollar savings bond and Evelyn Burks posed behind cake for her birthday party
